name: Globular Steampunk
description:
Jalla Jalla Metelkova series 03


I had no idea where to go once i arrived in Ljubljana, but a friend of mine suggest me to go to this place, from the entrance its look like a ghetto, murals were everywhere, and once i got inside, I was mesmerized with the building they have there, it was a military barrack before, and they turn it into alternative cultural house project. The garden was full of interesting art installation, and i got lucky, to documenting some they have at there.


4240 × 2832 px Shot on Fujifilm XT-20 in Ljubljana, Slovenia 2017
